name: flwrs
description: My story is similar to many stories, but important to me. In the spring of 2020 at the first lockdown, I had a lot of anxiety and fear. Panic attacks, broken sleep patterns, eating disorder, all these things. And I began to look for something to direct my attention to, instead of things that I can't control and change. So I started drawing after a long break. This is the first of those drawings
